♪Waiting so long for your return♪

00:14:09.825 --> 00:14:17.113
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

00:14:17.613 --> 00:14:22.525
♪If the clear sky is torn
by storm and rain one day♪

00:14:22.875 --> 00:14:25.675
♪Tears will flow♪

00:14:26.813 --> 00:14:32.450
♪I will still wait here with no regrets♪

00:14:33.125 --> 00:14:40.313
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

00:14:40.850 --> 00:14:48.000
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

00:14:48.600 --> 00:14:53.288
♪In the amber desert,
you turn away with tears in your eyes♪

00:14:53.650 --> 00:14:57.075
♪I'll welcome you back in a red dress♪

